claim.claim-text:
1. A plectrum sleeve comprising:
a sleeve body sliding to a human's finger;
an extending sheet extending from an edge of an end of the sleeve body;
a plectrum piece extending from an end of the extending sheet;
wherein the sleeve body is slid to a finger with the extending sheet attached to a tip of the finger and the plectrum piece located in a front of a nail; and
at least one clamp unit capable of clamping the sleeve body to tightly fix the plectrum sleeve to the finger.
